headline: GOP to Phase Out Biden Energy Credits to Pay for Tax Cuts
summary: (Bloomberg) -- House Republicans are proposing to eliminate a tax credit for electric vehicles and phase out incentives to develop clean-energy projects to help pay for President Donald Trump’s massive tax package. headline: First Solar (NasdaqGS:FSLR) Revises Annual Guidance Downward
summary: First Solar (NasdaqGS:FSLR) reported its first-quarter 2025 results, which featured increased sales of $844 million but a decline in net income and EPS compared to the previous year, alongside a downward revision of its annual guidance. The market experienced a general upward trend, particularly with the U.S.-China tariff deal boosting the Dow Jones and tech-heavy indexes.
